Charles E. Bradley Jr.
Executive Compensation
As President & Chief Executive Officer, Director at CONSUMER PORTFOLIO SVCS INC, Charles E. Bradley Jr. made $4,215,600 in total compensation.  Of this total $995,000 was received as a salary, $2,800,000 was received as a bonus, $420,000 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $600 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


