Charles E. Brady Jr. - Wikipedia





















 






Charles E. Brady Jr.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Charles E. Brady, Jr.)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






This article's lead section may not adequately summarize key points of its contents. Please consider expanding the lead to provide an accessible overview of all important aspects of the article. Please discuss this issue on the article's talk page. (October 2009)




Charles Eldon Brady Jr.





NASA Astronaut


Nationality
American


Born
(1951-08-12)August 12, 1951
Pinehurst, North Carolina


Died
July 23, 2006(2006-07-23) (aged 54)



Other occupation

Medical Doctor


Rank
Captain, USN



Time in space

16d 21h 48m


Selection
1992 NASA Group


